%%{init: {'theme':'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Op as Operator
    participant SPA as SPA (calibration.js)
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>(parent_server.py)
    participant Cam as Camera node<br/>(camera_server.py)

    Note over Op,Cam: Pre-flight — marker coverage
    Op->>SPA: Open Calibration tab
    SPA->>Orch: GET /api/aruco/markers/coverage
    Orch->>Cam: GET /snapshot?cam=N (each camera)
    Cam-->>Orch: JPEG frame
    Orch->>Orch: _aruco_snapshot_detect
    Orch-->>SPA: per-cam visible IDs + recommendation pin
    SPA-->>Op: show coverage gaps

    opt intrinsic calibration (one-time per camera)
        Op->>SPA: Start intrinsic capture
        loop 15-30 frames
            SPA->>Orch: POST /api/cameras/fid/aruco/capture
            Orch->>Cam: GET /snapshot?cam=N
            Orch->>Orch: cv2.aruco.detectMarkers<br/>accumulate corners
        end
        SPA->>Orch: POST /api/cameras/fid/aruco/compute
        Orch->>Orch: cv2.calibrateCamera
        Orch->>Cam: POST /calibrate/intrinsic/save
        Cam-->>Orch: ok (persisted to disk)
        Orch-->>SPA: fx, fy, cx, cy, rmsError
    end

    Op->>SPA: Start stage-map solve
    SPA->>Orch: POST /api/cameras/fid/stage-map

    Note over Orch,Cam: Multi-snapshot aggregation
    loop maxSnapshots (default 6)
        Orch->>Cam: GET /snapshot?cam=N
        Cam-->>Orch: JPEG
        Orch->>Orch: detectMarkers<br/>keep largest per ID
    end

    Orch->>Cam: GET /calibrate/intrinsic?cam=N
    Cam-->>Orch: K or 404
    alt K available
        Orch->>Orch: intrinsic_source=calibrated
    else fallback
        Orch->>Orch: intrinsic_source=fov-estimate
    end

    Orch->>Orch: cv2.solvePnP SQPNP
    alt convergence
        Orch->>Orch: cv2.projectPoints<br/>RMS check
        Orch->>Orch: Rodrigues -> tilt/pan/roll<br/>store rotation + tvec
        Orch-->>SPA: ok, reprojectionRmsPx
        SPA-->>Op: show pose + match count
    else RMS > 5 or no convergence
        Orch->>Orch: try SOLVEPNP_ITERATIVE
        alt still fails
            Orch-->>SPA: error, matched count
            SPA-->>Op: "Add markers or reposition"
        end
    end
